{"tid":919673,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣/荃灣區 電結他招生2 (教rock 亦教jazz ,攻略五線譜同考試,不同風格一齊癲)","createTime":"2018-11-28T08:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T03:50:02.000Z","uid":166708,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0485b5bf2334edf197763391afd200d3c5303c2","tid":919673,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"對上個Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/530217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/530217</a><br />\n<br />\n入面有D 教學同簡介<br />\n<br />\n資歷: rockschool 8級電結他, 5級皇家鋼琴,五級樂理 地點: 青衣/荃灣<br />\n<br />\n實戰: 4年爵士大樂團, 一年兒童合唱團, jazz band 同各大大小小的酒店演出<br />\n<br />\n教學經驗: 2015 年 poly 音樂比賽冠軍 (份譜係我幫個學生編,幫佢執左個BASS,結他同鼓) 聽個學生講佢地攞冠軍之後畀紅線簽咗約<br />\n<br />\n數個學生達merit 成績,而且考試歌好高分<br />\n<br />\n教過兒童合唱團,幫佢地綵排演出<br />\n<br />\n教緊社區中心同琴行,社區中心教班由上一手教左兩年都唔熟open chord去到教左9個月教緊hotel california ;當中甚至有自閉同學習障礙都算學得好地地<br />\n<br />\n有教地區琴行&hellip;教緊自彈自唱,有個女仔幫佢編埋intro同掃法 <br />\n<br />\n聯絡方法: Tg :klguitar (第一堂試堂免費)<br />\n<br />\n對上個post 有巴打跟緊,由地獄級拍子去到已經好準同岩touching 去到自已寫緊solo 同挑戰緊考試&hellip;希望佢來年一帆風順<br />\n<br />\n亦有人想玩jazz 學到可以去酒吧玩&hellip;果個BRO 已經征服autumn leave, all of me 同blue bossa , 重記得岩岩收果時拍子勁唔穩,依然jamming 已經穩陣, 識解chord同識用dorian 同lydian 去處理jazz<br />\n<br />\n都高興有部分有音樂底的巴打搵我學結他&hellip;當中不缺8級琴行底的人<br />\n<br />\n當中已經能應付funky free jamming <br />\n<br />\n而由零開始已經開始轟轟轟同迫緊佢地duo 去學jamming 同學solo<br />\n<br />\n我應該唔算傳統Rock 老師,堂堂練歌only<br />\n<br />\n學習系統: 教歌,教jamming ,教licks,寫solo,解樂理, 教不同風格, 特別係jazz 呢類比較難的風格,會迫學校學五線譜, 當然都有教考試<br />\n<br />\n第一堂試堂免費&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n今個post會打下 D教學啦&hellip;今次講五線譜點睇快D&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n至於D 左右手點大力D, F chord 點樣按得快D, 坊間大把教學我就唔寫啦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n希望我呢個招生post ,除左宣傳招生&hellip;都可以幫下有緣的你&hellip;亦可以隨便問問題<br />\n<br />\n視範(類近平時教學): <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kny4O9yTAcU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKny4O9yTAcU&d=FCE3QmlYR159ByaDNFjom7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=64366f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kny4O9yTAcU</a>"},{"pid":"cbd00b99e170c57c51d13d69d9f7a955635c2f6a","tid":919673,"uid":15403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"metal教唔教"},{"pid":"0f3af8512771e17adb95713d955d3d885fa0042e","tid":919673,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbd00b99e170c57c51d13d69d9f7a955635c2f6a","tid":919673,"uid":15403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"metal教唔教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"教啊 d 6 連音， 7 連音 metal 常見的癲拍子都會講<br />\n<br />\n7/8 呢類新派metal都會講<br />\n<br />\n如果有特定譜都可以拎來問<br />\n<br />\n個課程都會講metal 歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feab4ec503d86994c60c7eb8081579d100e6d891","tid":919673,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"幾勁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85985121b66106f1c46cbf4de869363b1c10bc45","tid":919673,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feab4ec503d86994c60c7eb8081579d100e6d891","tid":919673,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"幾勁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T05:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d7b8ee94def07ce81e1af404f16d6e41826c7b","tid":919673,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db367170cbc17df339a6f5e2d1a39ad4ea4d8dd2","tid":919673,"uid":72948,"like":0,"di